361
00:26:56,880 --> 00:27:03,000
Before I fail and get caught lying again, I must try to get by.

362
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:06,920
Grandpa, apart from your glasses,

363
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:09,394
I have another thing for you.

364
00:27:13,497 --> 00:27:15,140
Here you are.

365
00:27:15,140 --> 00:27:17,540
