375
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,610
But we still have a contract.

376
00:28:16,610 --> 00:28:17,943
Do you want to get fined?

377
00:28:17,943 --> 00:28:20,088
Just do that, Pete.

378
00:28:20,088 --> 00:28:22,427
Just take whatever you want.

379
00:28:34,530 --> 00:28:36,210
I think you should take a shower

380
00:28:36,210 --> 00:28:39,129
