385
00:29:04,810 --> 00:29:06,560
Wait.

386
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:07,810
Let's go.

387
00:29:07,810 --> 00:29:09,543
No, you don't have to do that.

388
00:29:09,543 --> 00:29:11,660
Just take him inside to rest. I'll take care of it.

389
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:13,490
Come sit on the couch.

390
00:29:17,186 --> 00:29:19,367
Sit here. I'll bring you some water.

391
00:29:19,367 --> 00:29:20,760
Sounds good.

392
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:01,315
I don't know how he is now.

393
00:30:27,690 --> 00:30:30,935
I think he must have already moved on for awhile now.

394
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:35,920
It's just I who hasn't let go of him.

395
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:53,510
A new pair of shoes that usually takes us to places far away...

396
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:57,895
sometimes brings us back to the same place.

397
00:31:32,420 --> 00:31:34,160
What's the matter, Mom?

398
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:36,420
Pam, are you busy now?

399
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:38,432
Please come to see me.

400
00:31:43,650 --> 00:31:46,020
Guys, please stand in line.

401
00:31:46,020 --> 00:31:48,587
Don't queue jumping those who came first.

402
00:31:48,587 --> 00:31:50,940
Please gather here.

403
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:54,100
Please gather around here.

404
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:56,220
Okay. Thank you so much.

405
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:58,099
Hello.

406
00:32:04,610 --> 00:32:06,410
Pete, you're here.

407
00:32:06,410 --> 00:32:08,000
What's going on?

408
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:12,010
They're here to see Donovan.

409
00:32:12,010 --> 00:32:15,170
I thought there was a casting today.

410
00:32:15,170 --> 00:32:18,370
Nope. They're here just to see Donovan.

411
00:32:18,370 --> 00:32:20,020
I'll get back to work.

412
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:24,215
Guys, please stand in line.

413
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:34,571
I told you I'm not in the mood to work.

414
00:32:39,650 --> 00:32:41,450
It's me.

415
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:47,209
I have to see him again.

416
00:32:57,080 --> 00:32:59,976
Why did you allow yourself to be like this?

417
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:03,554
What's the matter?

418
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:08,040
I have something to talk to you about.

419
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:09,840
Go ahead.

420
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:16,440
Take a shower, and then we can talk properly.

421
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,188
It's a long story.

422
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:14,280
I bought some food for you.

423
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,880
I'll put them on a plate.

424
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:19,488
Hey, don't.

425
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:22,500
You don't have to do anything for me anymore.

426
00:34:22,500 --> 00:34:25,082
You're no longer my manager.

427
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:37,730
If your mom asked you to talk me about going back to work,

428
00:34:37,730 --> 00:34:40,993
please don't. I'm not going.

429
00:34:42,160 --> 00:34:45,068
I don't want to work for her anymore.

430
00:34:46,940 --> 00:34:48,760
It's not about that.

431
00:34:50,450 --> 00:34:52,500
What is it?

432
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:55,600
