437
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:08,570
Some said they know her and can share information with us.

438
00:35:08,570 --> 00:35:16,137
But I don't know what is true and what is not.

439
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:21,690
I think you know it better than I do, so I want you to talk to them yourself.

440
00:35:21,690 --> 00:35:23,260
Where do I have to go?

441
00:35:23,260 --> 00:35:25,880
I asked them to meet at Mom's office.

442
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:28,270
- I'll go.
- Wait.

443
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:34,242
Are you sure you will go like this?

444
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,220
What's wrong?

445
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,578
