474
00:39:02,370 --> 00:39:04,070
Who?

475
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:09,911
Mr. Aood?

476
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:14,180
It must be him.

477
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:16,609
What did he say to you?

478
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:20,170
If you don't tell me,

479
00:39:20,170 --> 00:39:22,060
I will cut you with this razor.

480
00:39:22,060 --> 00:39:24,050
