481
00:39:24,050 --> 00:39:26,487
You must figure it out for yourself.

482
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:40,280
All right.

483
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:44,737
I won't ask you anymore if you feel uncomfortable answering.

484
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:49,220
But I'm still curious anyway.

485
00:39:49,220 --> 00:39:52,334
You disappeared like that and didn't explain anything to me

486
00:39:52,334 --> 00:39:55,713
while that day we almost...

