527
00:43:10,463 --> 00:43:12,719
I have a way.

528
00:43:17,410 --> 00:43:19,802
Be quiet, please.

529
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:25,010
Before Donovan interviews you today,

530
00:43:25,010 --> 00:43:27,586
