531
00:43:27,586 --> 00:43:29,747
If you're ready, raise your hand!

532
00:43:29,747 --> 00:43:31,533
Hands up.

533
00:43:35,626 --> 00:43:37,300
You.

534
00:43:37,300 --> 00:43:39,360
